data.description:
It has 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, bonus room in the garage, living room and den, dining area, and eat-in kitchen, small office space and spacious front & back yard. Plus, a washer/dryer hook-up. Move-in availability is February 8, 2023. This property is also for rent by owner. Security deposit - $2,700 + Rent $2,700 to move in. Pet fee is $300 non-refundable for 1-3 pets, and for 4 or more pets is a $500 non-refundable fee upfront.
Easy walking to public transit, schools, dining, shopping and great neighborhood.

Renter responsible for electric, waste pick-up, lawncare, water, and minor house repairs. No smoking allowed inside house. No illegal drugs allowed on the premises. Pets are allowed.
